fields.label_text: Travelling chest containing spirit bottles and drinking glasses , engraved and gilt glass  Bohemia and Spain (San Ildefonso), mid-18th century and later    Gift of Percy Woods, Esq.  (C.76 to C.103-1914)     The chest contains mid-18th century Bohemian spirit flasks together with eight glasses made about 1760-75 at La Granja glasshouse, San Ildefonso, Spain: these are C.94 to C.99, and C.101 and C.102-1914.   .

fields.descriptive_line: Travelling chest containing mid 18th century Bohemian spirit bottles, and eight drinking glasses made about 1760-75 at La Granja glasshouse, San Ildefonso, Spain
